Gravatar Helper

A CakePHP Helper for displaying Gravatars

INSTALLATION
------------

Copy gravatar.php to your app/views/helpers directory

CONFIGURATION
---------------

In your controller, add the Gravatar Helper to your $helpers array

    public $helpers = array('Gravatar');

USAGE
---------------

The following examples demonstrate various uses in your view:

    echo $this->Gravatar->image('robert.love@signified.com.au');

    echo $this->Gravatar->image('robert.love@signified.com.au', array('size' => 200));

    echo $this->Gravatar->image('robert.love@signified.com.au', array('size' => 100), array('alt' => 'Robert Love'));

